  "summary": "clean-my-pc exfiltrates host information to hardcoded attacker endpoint",
  "details": "The package's collect.js imports os, fs, http, https, and child_process and POSTs host information including os.hostname() and os.homedir() to the hardcoded endpoint http://aab.sportsontheweb.net. The package masquerades as a PC cleaning utility but its actual behavior is system reconnaissance and data exfiltration to an attacker-controlled domain. Filesystem probing via fs.existsSync paired with HTTP POST to a non-publisher, non-registry endpoint indicates targeted host enumeration for follow-on attacks.",
